त्","m":"greeted"}]},{"v":39,"dev":"तंसमुत्थाप्यकाकुत्स्थश्चिरस्याक्षिरथंगतम् अङ्केभरतमारोप्यमुदितःपरिषस्वजे ।","trans":"Kakuthsa Rama happily lifting up Bharata, who came into his sight after long, on to his thigh embraced him.","words":[{"d":"काकुत्स्थः","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"चिराय","m":"after long"},{"d":"अक्षिपथम्","m":"who came in his sight"},{"d":"गतम्","m":"arrived at"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"भरतम्","m":"Bharata"},{"d":"समुत्थाप्य","m":"lifting up"},{"d":"अङ्कम्","m":"thigh"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"lifted to"},{"d":"परिषस्वजे","m":"embraced"}]},{"v":40,"dev":"ततोलक्ष्मणमासाद्यवैदेहीं च परन्तपः अथाभ्यवादयप्रतीतोभरतोनामचाब्रवीत् ।","trans":"Then the tormentor of enemies, Bharata approached Lakshmana and then greeted Vaidehi and announced his name.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"परन्तपः","m":"tormentor of enemies"},{"d":"भरतः","m":"Bharata"},{"d":"प्रीतः","m":"lovingly"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"वैदेहीं च","m":"and Vaidehi"},{"d":"आसाद्य","m":"approached"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"अभ्यवादयत्","m":"greeted"},{"d":"नाम","m":"name"},{"d":"अब्रवीत् च","m":"announced"}]},{"v":41,"dev":"सुग्रीवंकेकयीपुत्रोजाम्बवन्तमथाङ्गदम् मैन्दं च द्विविदंनीलमृषभंपरिषस्वजे ।","trans":"Bharata, the son of Kaikeyi thereafter embraced Sugriva, Jambavantha, Angada, Mainda, Dwivivida, Nila and Rshaba.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"केकयीपुत्रः","m":"Kaikeyi's son"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"जाम्बवन्तम्","m":"Jambavantha"},{"d":"अङ्गदम्","m":"Angada"},{"d":"मैन्दम्","m":"Mainda"},{"d":"द्विविदंचैव","m":"and Dwivivida"},{"d":"नीलम्","m":"Nila"},{"d":"ऋषभम्","m":"Rshaba"},{"d":"परषस्वजे","m":"embraced"}]},{"v":42,"dev":"सुषेणं च नलंचैवगवाक्षंगन्धमादनम् शरभंपनसंचैवपरितःपरिषस्वजे ।","trans":"He embraced Sushena, Nala, Gavaksha, Gandhamadana, Sarabha, Panasa who were around.","words":[{"d":"सुषेणं च","m":"Sushena"},{"d":"नलंचैव","m":"Nala"},{"d":"गवाक्षम्","m":"Gavaksha"},{"d":"गन्धमादनम्","m":"Gandhamadana"},{"d":"शरभम्","m":"Sarabha"},{"d